high_descs: Turn around and move toward the sink next to the range.
Open the cabinet beneath the sink that is closest to the range, pick up the cup from the cabinet containing the green sponge, then close the cabinet door.
Turn around and move toward the door then turn left and move toward the refrigerator.

Open the refrigerator door, place the cup containing the sponge on the middle shelf to the left of the bowl, allow the cup to cool, open the refrigerator door, pick up the cup containing the sponge, and close the door.
Turn left and move to the dishwasher next to the sink then turn right and face the microwave.
Place the cup containing the sponge on the plate in the microwave to the right of the egg and close the microwave door.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled cup containing a sponge in the microwave.

high_descs: Open cabinet under the sink and pick up the mug with sponge in there.
Bring the mug with sponge to the fridge.
Chill the mug with sponge in the fridge.
Bring the mug with sponge to the microwave.
Put the mug with sponge in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug with sponge in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around, walk to the sink
Open the left cabinet door under the sink, take the green sponge and the cup out, close the cabinet
Turn around, walk to the refrigerator
Open the refrigerator, put the sponge and the cup in, close the refrigerator, open the refrigerator, take the cup and sponge out, close the refrigerator
